Package edu.sdsc.mmtf.spark.filters.demos

Demos of filter functions.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FilterByExperimentalMethods
    Example how to filter PDB entries by experimental methods.
    FilterByGroups
    This example demonstrates how to filter structures with specified groups (residues).
    FilterByPolymerChainType
    This example demonstrates how to filter the PDB by polymer chain type.
    FilterByResolution
    Example of reading an MMTF Hadoop Sequence file, filtering the entries by resolution, and counting the number of entries.
    FilterByRFree
    Example of reading an MMTF Hadoop Sequence file, filtering the entries by resolution, and counting the number of entries.
    FilterBySequenceRegex  
    FilterExclusivelyByLProteins
    This example demonstrates how to filter the PDB by polymer chain type.
    FilterProteinDnaComplexes
    This example demonstrates how to filter the PDB by polymer chain type.
    NotFilterExample
    Example how to wrap a filter in a NotFilter to negate a filter.
